query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('gis',
'magento',
'salesforce')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('adminhtml',
'carto',
'convert',
'coordinates',
'event-observer',
'geotiff-tiff',
'google-earth-engine',
'gps',
'json',
'magento-enterprise',
'overrides',
'point',
'print-composer',
'rest',
'validation')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name ilike '%her%';
